## 🎨 Color Cards

Let's create beautiful cards:

```elixir
name = "Your Name"
favorite_color = "blue"
age = 9

Kino.Markdown.new("""
<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            color: white;
            text-align: center;">
  <h1>🌟 #{name} 🌟</h1>
  <h2>I am #{age} years old</h2>
  <p style="font-size: 20px;">My favorite color is #{favorite_color}</p>
  <p style="font-size: 40px;">😊</p>
</div>
""")
```

