## 🏆 Challenge 2: Your Personal Page

Create a page about yourself with colors:

```elixir
Kino.Markdown.new("""
<div style="font-family: Arial; max-width: 600px;">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4); 
              padding: 40px; 
              text-align: center; 
              color: white; 
