```

## 🎮 Colorful Inputs

We can also ask for information with colors!

```elixir
color_input = Kino.Input.text("What's your favorite color?")
```

```elixir
color_input
```

```elixir
chosen_color = Kino.Input.read(color_input)

Kino.Markdown.new("""
<div style="background-color: #{chosen_color}; padding: 40px; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
  <h1 style="color: white; text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
    #{chosen_color} is a great color! 🎨
  </h1>
</div>
""")
```

